[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說初分說經卷上",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏傳法大師",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賜紫臣施護奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊往詣優樓頻螺耆年迦葉所，到彼處已。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉見佛世尊自遠而來，即白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善來，大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸有所須衣服飲食，我悉供給。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，世尊即謂迦葉言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今於汝此舍之中，止息一夜。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉白言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此舍非我所止之處，是我事火之舍。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一大龍，見止其中，彼龍具大神通，有大威力，汝今若止其中，恐彼侵害。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是世尊第二、第三謂迦葉言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「但令我今於此會中，止息一夜。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時彼迦葉亦復再三而白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大龍居中，恐彼侵害，汝今宜應信受我語。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763a29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今不應多與其言，起悲愍心，決定轉故。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已，即入火舍，以僧伽梨衣四疊，安置淨草之處，然後世尊加趺而坐。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，彼龍心生瞋恚，乃吐煙焰，充塞其舍。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊即入火界三昧，亦出煙焰，周匝其舍，都成一聚大火熾焰。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼龍復出青、黃、赤、白種種色相大惡火焰，世尊亦出青、黃、赤、白種種色焰。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，優樓頻螺耆年迦葉與自眷屬，於其火舍，周匝旋轉已，作如是言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此大沙門，最上色相，先不聽我言，必為龍所害。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b11_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，世尊以神通力，於須臾間，彼龍威光，自然收攝。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉知佛世尊亦得神通，盡其夜分，隨其所應，佛現神通，時即往觀察，乃見其龍，威光漸少，世尊光明，轉復熾盛。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊於明旦時，攝伏彼龍，入其鉢中，持示迦葉言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是火舍中龍，我已攝伏。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b17_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此龍有大威力，若諸凡夫，即不能入其舍。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時彼迦葉即生歎異，乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復次，優樓頻螺耆年迦葉，欲於日初分時作事火法，即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此大沙門，有大威力，具大神通，乃至大威力，龍亦能攝伏。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今但於日初分時，作事火法，彼大沙門，於日後分時，應作神通事。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，世尊知彼迦葉信佛神通，世尊即為攝神通力，而彼迦葉於日初分，得作大事已，即生歎異，乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763b28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又復，迦葉欲於日後分時作事火法，即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此大沙門，有大威力，具大神通，乃至大威力，龍亦能攝伏，我今但於日後分時，作事火法。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼大沙門，於日初分時，應作神通事。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，世尊知彼迦葉信佛神通，世尊即為攝神通力。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼迦葉於日後分時，得作大事已，即生歎異，乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又復，迦葉別作然火法種種施作，皆不能然，復以乾木，投擲其中，及以乾草、乾瞿摩夷、蘇油等物。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所應用者，悉擲其內，復作不善相，出是呪言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「伊梨薩哥　多梨薩哥　一切能燒，此何不然？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c12_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是呪已，火亦不然。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此大沙門，具大神通，有大威力，乃至大威力，龍亦能攝伏，我以何物，當為供養？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，世尊知彼迦葉信佛神通，世尊即為起神通力，其火乃然。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉即生歎異，乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又復，迦葉既作法已，欲滅其火，種種施作，不能息滅，乃取淨土，傾擲其中，復投以灰，乃灑以水，亦作不善相，出是呪言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「伊梨薩哥　多梨薩哥　一切燒已，此何不滅？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c22_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是呪已，火亦不滅。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉，即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此大沙門，具大神通，有大威力，乃至大威力，龍亦能攝伏，我以何物，當為供養？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時世尊，知彼迦葉信佛神通，世尊即為攝神通力，其火乃滅。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉，即生歎異，乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0763c28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復次，迦葉於晝日分，而暫睡眠，世尊即化五百耆年，眾狀如迦葉，俱詣其所。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "化眾到已，高出其聲，互相戲笑。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉由戲笑聲，乃從睡覺，作是思惟：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今何故耽著睡眠？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "同梵行者，來亦不知。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時彼化眾咸讚是言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a04_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，迦葉普遍觀察，各各見其色相，乃作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a05_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「豈非大沙門神力所化邪？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼大沙門，具大神通，有大威力，乃至大威力，龍亦能攝伏，我以何物，當為供養？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，世尊知彼迦葉信佛神通，世尊即為攝神通力，彼諸化眾忽然不見。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉即生歎異，乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊離彼迦葉住處，往詣泥連河岸，珂那聚落中阿惹播羅樹下。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊行時，體具威儀，容相可觀，既到彼已，而暫止息。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時迦葉即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等今時，亦往泥連河岸，作潔淨事水法，而大沙門亦復在彼。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已，即與眷屬，詣泥連河岸，到已忽見其水逆流，復作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此水逆流，豈非大沙門神通所作邪？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而此大沙門，具大神通，有大威力，乃至大威力，龍亦能攝伏，我以何物，當為供養？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，世尊知彼迦葉信佛神通，世尊乃為攝神通力，水即順流。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉即生歎異，乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又復，世尊漸次欲渡泥連河，往縛象聚落中，是時大雲忽起，暴雨澍流，河聲泛漲，如角貝響。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊爾時於急流中，徐緩而進，水分兩派，步步塵生。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉乃作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此大沙門，方涉中流，河水迅急，將非漂沒。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764a28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念時，乃見世尊，於急流中，水分兩派，步步塵生，漸至其岸。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即生歎異：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「希有難得！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此大沙門名，我於諸世間，曾所未聞。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉爾時乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉見佛如是等神通事已，轉發最上清淨信心，深生愛樂，乃發是言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能作如是神通事業，我以何物，當為供養？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊既至彼岸於縛象聚落中，而乃止息。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即於是夜，東方持國天王，來詣佛所，恭敬禮足，彼身光明，廣大照耀。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉是夜覩斯光已，至明旦時，往詣佛所，到已白言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夜中何故東方光來廣大照耀？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊告言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「夜中所現東方光者，是彼持國天王，來禮我足，彼身光明，照耀如是。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉爾時即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼之名字，我等雖聞，而不能見，況復能來禮沙門足？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我觀是事，希有難得。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第二夜中，南方增長天王，來詣佛所，恭敬禮足，彼身光明，廣大照耀。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉是夜覩斯光已，至明旦時，往詣佛所，到已白言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夜中何故南方光來廣大照耀？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊告言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「夜中所現南方光者，是彼增長天王，來禮我足，彼身光明，照耀如是。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉爾時即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b22_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼之名字，我等雖聞，而不能見，況復能來禮沙門足？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我觀是事，希有難得。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第三夜中，西方廣目天王，來詣佛所，恭敬禮足，彼身光明，廣大照耀。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉是夜覩斯光已，至明旦時，往詣佛所，到已白言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夜中何故西方光來廣大照耀？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊告言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764b29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「夜中所現西方光者，是彼廣目天王，來禮我足，彼身光明，照耀如是。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉爾時即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼之名字，我等雖聞，而不能見，況復能來禮沙門足？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我觀是事，希有難得。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第四夜中，北方多聞天王，來詣佛所，恭敬禮足，彼身光明，廣大照耀。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉是夜覩斯光已，至明旦時，往詣佛所，到已白言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夜中何故北方光來廣大照耀？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊告言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「夜中所現北方光者，是彼多聞天王，來禮我足，彼身光明，照耀如是。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉爾時即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼之名字，我等雖聞，而不能見，況復能來禮沙門足？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我觀是事，希有難得。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第五夜中，上方帝釋天王，來詣佛所，恭敬禮足，彼身光明，廣大照耀。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉是夜覩斯光已，至明旦時，往詣佛所，到已白言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夜中何故上方光來廣大照耀？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊告言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「夜中所現上方光者，是彼帝釋天主，來禮我足，彼身光明，照耀如是。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉爾時即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼之名字，我等雖聞，而不能見，況復能來禮沙門足？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我觀是事，希有難得。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」第六夜中，四方四大天王、上方帝釋天主，俱詣佛所，恭敬禮足，四王身光，四方互照；",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋身光，上方照耀。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然彼諸光，悉於世尊三摩地光中之所收攝。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉是夜覩斯光已，至明旦時，往詣佛所，到已白言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c26_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夜中何故四方光來，及彼上方光來照耀？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊告言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「夜中所現四方光者，是彼四方天王；",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c28_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上方光者，是帝釋天主；",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0764c29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "俱來禮足，彼諸身光，照耀如是。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉爾時即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「五方俱來，禮沙門足，我觀是事，希有難得。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃發淨信：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我出家心，豈可止耶！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復次，世尊謂迦葉言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今為我，於菴摩勒林中，取彼菓來。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉以佛威神力故，如言即取持以奉佛。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊又言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝於呵梨勒林中，取彼藥來。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉如言取以奉佛。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊又言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝於贍部樹，先取其菓，次復可取隨應知者種種菓來。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉如言取以奉佛。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊又言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝於北俱盧洲，取彼飯來。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉如言取以奉佛。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a10_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊又言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝於三十三天中，取彼曼陀羅華來。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉如言取以奉佛。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，迦葉知佛世尊有如是等種種神通，轉復發起最上淨信。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊知彼心已，於迦葉前，復以神力，以虛空中，別見身相，起三威儀：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂住威儀、行步威儀、加趺坐威儀。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是所現諸威儀相，皆悉迅疾，如履急流，是相亦然；",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又於空中，化現眾寶，所成樓閣；",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復普現，黃金色相。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊現如是等諸神通已，還攝神力，本相如故。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時迦葉，常於年中，而擇一日，於自住處，作祀天會。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有摩伽陀國王舍大城頻婆娑羅王，及其國中一切人民，咸來赴會。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼迦葉，知設會時至，還本住處，乃作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我常所設祀天施會，今正是時，王及人民，咸悉來集。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼大沙門，面相平滿，遠離顰蹙，無復恚怒，出善語言，見者歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此最上善人，若來我舍，我祀天會，何能施作？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765a28_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時世尊，知彼心念已，即現神力，往北俱盧洲，如常乞食，還詣雪山邊，安坐而食，食已於彼作草菴舍，止息一夜。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼迦葉，祀天既畢，設會亦周，飲食所須，而尚豐溢。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉見已，即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼大沙門，今時若來，我當授食。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b04_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊知其念已，從虛空中來現其前。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉見已，作如是言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善來，大沙門！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我昨設會，汝何不來？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊答言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「知汝起念，故我不來。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b07_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊即為如念而說。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉復言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝於今日，何故乃來？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊答言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「亦知汝念，欲授我食，故我斯來。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，迦葉即作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「希有難得！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此大沙門，知我心意，此必同我，亦得阿羅漢。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊知其所念，即時謂言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「迦葉！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝非阿羅漢，不知阿羅漢法。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉聞已，復作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「希有！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b13_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "希有！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此大沙門，若心若意，若尋若伺，皆悉能知。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已，頭面著地，前禮佛足白言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b15_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今歸佛，出家受具足戒，惟願善逝，哀愍攝受。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「迦葉！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今不應投佛出家。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b17_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩伽陀國王及人民，皆悉宗敬、供養於汝，汝於親屬知識眾中，是最善人，宜應今時審自思忖。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「莫作是說！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫作是說！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我於世尊所，生極喜心，發勝愛樂，豈復審思，我今決定歸佛出家。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我出家已，於沙門婆羅門外道眾中，摧伏一切譏毀過失者，執持勝幢，於王舍大城中，次第經行，表示我優樓頻螺耆年迦葉，能於世尊清淨法中而得解脫，是故我今決定歸佛出家。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惟願世尊，哀愍攝受。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「迦葉！",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝能決定歸佛出家者，斯為甚善，然汝今時，亦應與自眷屬而共評議。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765b29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，迦葉如佛教勅，即與眷屬而相議言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765c01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝等當知，佛大沙門，具大神通，有大威力，一切見者，咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765c02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我於佛所，深發最上清淨信心，我今決定歸佛出家。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765c04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」諸眷屬言：",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765c04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我師聖者尚能如是發輕利心，我等諸人豈不出家？",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765c05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故今時，亦各樂欲，歸佛出家。",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765c06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說初分說經卷上",
        "from": "T14n0498_001:0765c07_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]